Package com.turo.pushy.apns.server

Interface PushNotificationHandlerFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcceptAllPushNotificationHandlerFactory, ValidatingPushNotificationHandlerFactory
    public interface PushNotificationHandlerFactory
    A push notification handler factory constructs PushNotificationHandler instances when a mock APNs server accepts a new connection. Handlers created by the factory control how the server responds to the push notifications it receives.
    Since:
    0.12

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      PushNotificationHandler buildHandler​(SSLSession sslSession)
      Constructs a new push notification handler that will process notifications from a single connection to a mock server.
